1180
01:41:04,013 --> 01:41:06,015
I think that the folks from Eversource have already

1181
01:41:06,482 --> 01:41:08,663
reiterated the fact that they would be more than willing to do that.

1182
01:41:08,863 --> 01:41:24,232
And as such, you know, Mr. Zamparelli is the Eversource Community Relations Specialist for our municipality, and he can be reached at William.Zamparelli, Z-A-M-P-A-R-E-L-L-I, at Eversource.com.

1183
01:41:24,292 --> 01:41:33,238
