01:41:49,817 --> 01:41:51,659
I only have two simple questions.

1191
01:41:52,799 --> 01:41:59,644
If they researched an existing route, with all those manhole covers out there, there's no existing route they can put their lines through?

1192
01:42:00,825 --> 01:42:03,667
