1197
01:42:20,914 --> 01:42:25,456
So now you have the bridge a block away, and you have the power line another block away.

1198
01:42:27,276 --> 01:42:31,017
So you've got to figure out, because that area is going to be so congested.

1199
01:42:32,137 --> 01:42:34,418
The only thing is, who's going to be the superpower there?

1200
01:42:35,042 --> 01:42:35,422
Exactly.

1201
01:42:35,802 --> 01:42:44,006
I think one of the goals that they've had is to engage an outside traffic consultant who's going to analyze.

1202
01:42:44,407 --> 01:42:57,453
That's one of the particular areas that needs a strong analysis because of the impact of the ongoing bridge construction as it affects the development of the trenching.

1203
01:42:57,833 --> 01:43:01,475
The only thing is these traffic consultants, they don't live in the city.

1204
01:43:02,764 --> 01:43:08,186
They may come at a real slow time and not come during rush hour.

1205
01:43:08,986 --> 01:43:13,248
I mean, that traffic backs up up Main Street, up past George Street and beyond.

1206
01:43:13,608 --> 01:43:13,828
Yes.

1207
01:43:14,388 --> 01:43:16,409
You know, trying to make the left on Mystic Ave.

1208
01:43:17,629 --> 01:43:27,933
So what's going to happen now when they close that bridge, move it over, and you've got the construction in Main Street, in Mystic, and then you have a block away, you have the bridge?

1209
01:43:29,333 --> 01:43:32,094
The gentleman is taking notes on that as we speak.

1210
01:43:33,012 --> 01:43:35,454
uh, to make that as part of their, uh, research.

